<div class='media__message'>
<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>세쓰 버클리</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/seth_berkley_the_troubling_reason_why_vaccines_are_made_too_late_if_they_re_made_at_all?language=ko' lang='ko'>
이미 개발된 백신이 너무 늦게 생산되는 골치 아픈 이유
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Aug 2015
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Informative, Persuasive
</span>
</span>
</div>
